        Serving All of Bergen County, NJ &bull; 100% Virtual
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold font-heading text-white mb-4">CPA &amp; Accounting Services in Bergen County, NJ</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 mb-8">ProAxis delivers expert tax preparation, tax planning, bookkeeping, and business advisory to Bergen County businesses and residents — all virtually, all on your schedule.</p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
        <a href="/contact/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-7 py-3.5 rounded-lg font-semibold text-white" style="background-color: #22C55E;">Schedule Free Consultation</a>
        <a href="tel:+12018002330" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-7 py-3.5 rounded-lg font-semibold text-white border-2 border-white/40">Call (201) 800-2330</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12 lg:py-16">

    <!-- Bergen County Business Landscape -->
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold font-heading mb-5" style="color: #1C1C1E;">Bergen County's Business Landscape</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Bergen County is New Jersey's most populous county, home to more than 950,000 residents spread across 70 municipalities. It sits directly across the Hudson River from New York City, and that geographic reality shapes everything about its economy — from the massive commuter population that flows into Manhattan each morning, to the dense concentration of corporate campuses, professional offices, and service businesses that cluster around the county's major Route corridors.</p>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">The county's commercial heart beats in several distinct nodes. <strong>Hackensack</strong>, the county seat, hosts Bergen County's government complex, a major healthcare corridor anchored by Hackensack University Medical Center, and a revitalizing Main Street commercial district. <strong>Paramus</strong> is in a category of its own — home to Garden State Plaza and Westfield, it generates more retail sales per square mile than almost anywhere else in the United States, drawing corporate retail headquarters, auto dealerships, and a sprawling Route 17 and Route 4 commercial ecosystem. <strong>Fort Lee</strong>, perched at the New Jersey approach to the George Washington Bridge, serves as a gateway community for NYC workers and is home to a thriving Korean-American business community with import/export, beauty supply, restaurant, and professional service enterprises.</p>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">The northern and western municipalities tell a different story — one of affluence, executive talent, and high-net-worth households. Communities like <strong>Ridgewood</strong>, <strong>Wyckoff</strong>, <strong>Upper Saddle River</strong>, and <strong>Allendale</strong> feature some of the highest median household incomes in New Jersey. Residents here frequently hold stock options, deferred compensation arrangements, real estate investment portfolios, and retirement accounts that demand sophisticated, year-round tax planning rather than once-a-year tax filing. The southern corridor — encompassing <strong>Teaneck</strong>, <strong>Englewood</strong>, <strong>Hasbrouck Heights</strong>, <strong>Rutherford</strong>, <strong>Fair Lawn</strong>, and <strong>Garfield</strong> — offers a mosaic of diverse working communities, manufacturing heritage, hospitality businesses, and first-generation entrepreneurialism.</p>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-8">Across all these communities runs a common thread: Bergen County residents and businesses face tax complexity well above the national average. High property values, elevated state income taxes, and the proximity to New York City create layered filing obligations that reward proactive planning.</p>

    <!-- Map -->
    <div class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg border border-gray-200 mb-10">
      <iframe
        src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3014.5!2d-74.0776!3d40.8598!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x0%3A0x0!2sHasbrouck+Heights%2C+NJ+07604!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sus!4v1"
        width="100%"
        height="300"
        style="border:0;"
        allowfullscreen=""
        loading="lazy"
        title="ProAxis CPA office location in Hasbrouck Heights NJ"
