    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-8">We also serve clients throughout the rest of Bergen County — including Mahwah, Ramsey, Westwood, Dumont, Bergenfield, Closter, Cresskill, Demarest, Emerson, Glen Rock, Harrington Park, Haworth, Hillsdale, Ho-Ho-Kus, Leonia, Lodi, Maywood, Midland Park, Montvale, Northvale, Norwood, Oakland, Old Tappan, Park Ridge, Rochelle Park, Saddle Brook, Saddle River, South Hackensack, Tenafly, Township of Washington, Upper Saddle River, Waldwick, Westwood, Wood-Ridge, and Wyckoff. If you're in Bergen County, ProAxis is your CPA.</p>

    <!-- Why Virtual CPA Makes Sense for Bergen County -->
    <div class="rounded-2xl p-8 mb-10" style="background-color: #F7F8FA;">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold font-heading mb-5" style="color: #1C1C1E;">Why a Virtual CPA Makes Sense for Bergen County</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">If you've ever tried to get a 9 AM Tuesday appointment at a traditional accounting firm in Hackensack or Paramus, you know the drill: limited availability, long wait times during tax season, and the obligation to drive across town — often in Bergen County traffic — to drop off a folder of documents.</p>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">ProAxis works differently. Our fully virtual model was designed for the way Bergen County professionals and business owners actually work. You share documents securely through our encrypted client portal. Meetings happen over video call, scheduled at your convenience. Questions get answered quickly — not in three weeks when your file works its way up the pile.</p>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">For Bergen County's large commuter population, this matters enormously. If you're on a 7:15 AM bus to Manhattan, you don't have time to take a morning off for a CPA appointment. With ProAxis, your accounting relationship fits your life, not the other way around.</p>
      <p class="text-gray-700">And because we're based right here in Hasbrouck Heights, we understand the local context — NJ business taxes, Bergen County commercial real estate, the specific industries that drive the county's economy — in a way that a generic national tax chain simply cannot replicate.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Services Section -->
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold font-heading mb-5" style="color: #1C1C1E;">Our CPA Services for Bergen County Clients</h2>
    <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-10">
      {[
        { name: "Tax Preparation", link: "/tax-services/tax-preparation/", desc: "Individual and business federal and NJ state tax returns, including multistate filings for NYC commuters." },
        { name: "Tax Planning", link: "/tax-services/tax-planning/", desc: "Year-round strategies to minimize your NJ income tax, maximize deductions, and plan for life events." },
